        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(status): warm model context-window cache before /status reads it",
        "body": "## Problem\n\n\\/status\\ shows \\200K\\ (DEFAULT_CONTEXT_TOKENS) for any model discovered from the provider catalog, regardless of the model's actual context window.\n\n## Root Cause\n\n**Four** independent gaps kept MODEL_CONTEXT_TOKEN_CACHE empty when \\/status\\ read it:\n\n1. **No startup warming**: \\server-startup-early.ts\\ had no cache warming call\n2. **prepareContextWindowCache short-circuit**: \\skipRuntimeConfigLoad=true\\ blocked even async warming\n3. **Status explicitly disabled warming**: \\status-text.ts\\ passed \\^GllowAsyncLoad: false\\\n4. **CLI status also disabled warming**: \\status.summary.ts\\ passed \\^GllowAsyncLoad: false\\ in BOTH config-model and session-row calls\n5. **Import bypass**: \\status.summary.runtime.ts\\ imported raw cache from \\context-resolution.js\\ instead of warming wrapper from \\context.ts\\\n\n## Fix (6 files)\n\n| File | Change | Gap Closed |\n|------|--------|-----------|\n| \\src/gateway/server-startup-early.ts\\ | Add \\\u000boid ensureContextWindowCacheLoaded()\\ at startup | #1 |\n| \\src/agents/context.ts\\ | Fire async warming when \\skipRuntimeConfigLoad=true\\ and \\^GllowAsyncLoad !== false\\ | #2 |\n| \\src/status/status-text.ts\\ | Remove \\^GllowAsyncLoad: false\\ | #3 |\n| \\src/commands/status.summary.ts\\ | Remove \\^GllowAsyncLoad: false\\ (both config-model and session-row call sites) | #4 |\n| \\src/commands/status.summary.runtime.ts\\ | Import from \\context.js\\ (warming wrapper) | #5 |\n| \\src/agents/context.lookup.test.ts\\ | 4 regression tests | Coverage |\n\n## Design Notes\n\n- **Fire-and-forget**: Uses \\\u000boid\\ matching existing \\primeRemoteSkillsCache()\\\n- **Backward-compatible**: \\^GllowAsyncLoad !== false\\ correctly distinguishes \\undefined\\ (fire warming) from \\\false\\ (skip)\n- **No slash-model behavior change**: Does not touch \\status-message.ts\\ (unlike superseded PR #92772)\n- **Startup warming + on-demand warming**: Covers both Gateway \\/status\\ and CLI \\openclaw status\\ paths\n\n## Related\n\n- Closes #92760\n- Supersedes #92772 (narrower scope)",
        "branch": "fix/context-window-clean",
